            <title><![CDATA[【信息】关于组织2026届本科毕业生图像采集（第三批） 工作的通知]]></title>
            <link>https://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/cms/article/view.do?type=posts&amp;id=eec18a7b9b43f62c019cbd455508005e</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">scut-jw-eec18a7b9b43f62c019cbd455508005e</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 08:25:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>类型:</strong> 信息 | <strong>日期:</strong> 2026.03.05 | <a href="https://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/cms/article/view.do?type=posts&id=eec18a7b9b43f62c019cbd455508005e">查看原文</a></p><hr><div class="content">



<p style="text-align:center"><br/></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">各院（系）：</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">毕业生图像采集工作是学生学历电子注册工作中的关键环节，拍摄的照片将用于相关学历、学位证书制作，并上报教育部作为学历、学位的重要信息进行电子注册及上网查询。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">为保障图像真实性，教育部近期就高校新生、毕业生图像采集工作提出相关要求：</span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">各类高等教育新生、毕业生图像采集，学生不得提交预先准备好的图片</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">。2025年11月15日和2025<span style="font-family:仿宋">年1</span>2月27日<span style="font-family:仿宋">已完成第一、第二批2026届本科毕业生图像采集。</span>截至目前，仍有部分学生未完成采集工作。<span style="font-family:仿宋">现将我校202</span>6届本科毕业生图像采集（第三批）安排通知如下，请相关毕业生做好准备工作，务必准时参加：</span></p><p><strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">一、图像采集安排</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">1.参加本次图像采集的学生范围：我校2026届未完成采集的本科毕业班学生（</span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">2025年11月15日和</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">202</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">5</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">年1</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">2</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">月</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">27</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">日</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">已完成采集的学生不再安排采集；</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">往年已采集过毕业相片且已上传学信网的同学无需参加本次采集</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">）。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">2.图像采集的时间：</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">2026年3月5日至2026年4月2日</span></p><p><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">3. 图像采集方式：</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">线上采集。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">访问方式1：手机浏览器直接输入网址：https://scut.qmr.net.cn</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">访问方式2：微信扫描对应二维码</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"> <img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701419332004606.png" title="1772701419332004606.png"/></span></p><p><strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">二、图像采集收费</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;line-height:150%;font-size:19px">图像信息采集收费标准为<span style="font-family:仿宋">每人15 元（含2寸数码彩照 8张）</span>，学生通过线上自行缴纳。</span></p><p><strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">三、工作联系人</span></strong></p><p style="line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;line-height:150%;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:19px">1.采集过程中如有疑问请联系客服</span></strong><strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;line-height:150%;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:19px">。</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">（1）电话咨询：</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">联系电话：0871-65360281、18987457023；</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">服务时间：周一至周日（国家节假日除外），上午9:00-11:30、下午13:30-17:30。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">（2）微信公众号咨询：微信搜索并关注“启梦瑞校园摄影服务”公众号/服务号，点击右下角“联系我们”即可咨询。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;line-height:150%;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:19px"> </span></strong></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;line-height:150%;font-size:19px">2.如发现照片不一致、信息有误等问题，请联系：</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;line-height:150%;font-size:19px">五山校区学生<span style="font-family:仿宋">：黄老师，87110736，huangsx@scut.edu.cn</span></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;line-height:150%;font-size:19px">大学城校区学生：凌老师，81182790<span style="font-family:仿宋">，zmling@scut.edu.cn</span></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;line-height:150%;font-size:19px">广州国际校区学生<span style="font-family:仿宋">：黄老师，81181639，huangsy@scut.edu.cn</span></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;line-height:150%;font-size:19px">外籍留学生：高老师，81182570，</span><a href="mailto:gao_hongyao@163.com"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;line-height:150%;font-size:19px">gao_hongyao@163.com</span></a></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;line-height:150%;font-size:16px"> </span></p><p style="text-align:right"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">本科生院</span></p><p style="text-align:right"><a href="http://www2.scut.edu.cn/gzic/2018/1031/c30300a450394/page.htm" style="text-decoration: underline; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 19px;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">广州国际校区教学事务办公室</span></a></p><p style="text-align:right"><a href="http://www.scut.edu.cn/sie/" style="text-decoration: underline; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 19px;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">国际教育学院</span></a></p><p style="text-align:right"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">2026年3月5日</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px"> </span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">附件1：</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">远程采集系统操作步骤及注意事项</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">一、</span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">核心原则</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">（一）“四不要”（严格规避，避免审核失败）</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">？不要自拍：</span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 19px">需由他人协助拍摄</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">，确保采集规范照片。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">？不要开美颜：</span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 19px">必须使用真实拍照模式，否则可能导致人像比对不通过。</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">？不要上传照片：</span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 19px">仅限现场拍照并实时上传，严禁翻拍纸质照片或屏幕电子照片。</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">？不要背景杂乱：</span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 19px">需选择干净背景，优先蓝色背景，白色墙面也可。</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">（二）“三要”（重点遵循，保障照片质量）</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">？要注意光线均匀：避开顶光、侧光、高光及曝光不足的情况</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">？要注意取景大小：拍摄半身人像，头顶及身体两侧需预留空白距离</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">？要拍正面人像：身体直立、人像居中、头部端正、两耳对称、双眼平视；双肩水平</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">二、线上采集方法</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">1.访问方式：</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">手机浏览器直接输入网址：https://scut.qmr.net.cn</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">微信扫描对应二维码</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701500989074170.png" title="1772701500989074170.png"/> </span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"> </span></p><p><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">2. 采集环节：</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">进入系统后，选择“直接扫采集码”或“打开采集码图片”进入采集环节；</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><img alt="image.png" height="532" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701531155076384.png" style="width: 312px; height: 532px;" title="1772701531155076384.png" width="312"/> </span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"> </span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">若打开采集码图片识别失败，可将</span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">采集码照片</span></strong><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">（采集码获取方式详见附件2）</span></strong><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">保存至电脑桌面，或发送至另一部手机，再通过“直接扫采集码”方式进入拍照环节；</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">【重要提示1】：如遇上传图像无法显示，请按要求重新拍照上传</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">【重要提示2】：采集码需从“学信网”下载获取，详细操作流程可查看附件中的“采集码”下载操作指南</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">三、拍照要求与注意事项</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（一）取景方式</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">1.必须使用手机“竖屏”现场拍摄，建议以白墙为背景，且需由他人协助拍摄，严禁自拍；</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">2.取景标准要求参照下例示例图：</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:14px">       </span></p><p>                                     <img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701617540091950.png" title="1772701617540091950.png"/>                <img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701634230021166.png" title="1772701634230021166.png"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"> </span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（二）人像要求</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">需严格遵循以下规范，否则将影响审核结果：</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">1.姿态规范：头部与身体保持端正，面部表情自然、嘴巴自然闭合，双眼平视镜头，确保双眼连线与肩膀水平；</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">2.仪容仪表规范：</span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 19px">头发梳理整齐，不得遮挡耳朵和眉毛；禁止化浓妆；不得佩戴项链、耳环、头箍、发卡等饰品，且严禁佩戴带镜片的眼镜（含近视镜、墨镜、有色隐形眼镜等）。服饰着正装，避免奇装异服；</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">3.【不符合要求案例】</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">          <img alt="image.png" height="146" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701649080020360.png" style="width: 751px; height: 146px;" title="1772701649080020360.png" width="751"/> </span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">头发遮挡五官、眼镜反光/佩戴有色眼镜、佩戴饰品、开启美颜/瘦脸功能、嘴巴张开、脸部侧歪（两耳不对称）、衣物不整洁、衣物臃肿遮挡肩膀等。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">（三）光线与背景要求</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">1.光线要求：</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 19px">优先使用自然光拍摄，可选择室外、走廊或正对窗户的位置；</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 19px">确保面部无阴影、无高光，照片整体清晰明亮，避免出现模糊、曝光过度（画面发白）或曝光不足（画面发暗）的情况。</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">2.背景要求：</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">背景需平整、无杂物、无明显褶皱；</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 19px">禁止使用红色背景，衣物颜色与背景色需有明显区分度（区分度越大越好）；</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">为避免拍摄对象在背景墙形成阴影，可适当与背景墙保持一定距离。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">3.【不符合要求案例】</span></p><p>                   <img alt="image.png" height="131" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701669121035238.png" style="width: 758px; height: 131px;" title="1772701669121035238.png" width="758"/><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"> </span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">眼镜反光、面部“阴阳脸”、侧光照射、曝光过度、曝光不足、背景复杂、照片清晰度不足等。</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">四、审核结果相关说明</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">1.审核标准：照片是否合格，最终</span><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">以“人工审核结果”为准</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">；</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">2.人工审核申请：若多次提交照片均未通过系统自动审核，但拍摄者认为照片符合标准，可直接选择“下一步-人工审核”，无需重复拍照上传；</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">3.结果查询： </span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">查询时间：照片“上传成功”后72小时；</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">登录方式：输入学号+身份证号码后四位进入系统查询；</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">结果处理：</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">审核通过：等待照片上报学信网（约15个工作日后可登录学信网查看结果）；</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">审核失败：系统将告知不合格原因及修改建议，需按要求重新拍摄并上传。</span></p><p style=";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"> </span></p><p style=";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"> </span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">附件2：采集码获取方式</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">方法一</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">：</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">浏览器获取</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">（手机端和</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">PC</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">端流程一致）</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">1.登录学信网（</span><a href="https://www.chsi.com.cn/"><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(128, 0, 128); font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">https://www.chsi.com.cn/</span></a><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">），点击“学信档案”并登录。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701706125001121.png" title="1772701706125001121.png"/></p><p>                                                                             </p><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701716017038758.png" title="1772701716017038758.png"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"> </span><br/></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">2.点击进入“高等教育信息”菜单下的“学籍”。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701736267084827.png" title="1772701736267084827.png"/></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">3.选择学籍，点击“获取图像采集码”。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"> </span></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701760097002592.png" title="1772701760097002592.png"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701776424047501.png" title="1772701776424047501.png"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"> </span><br/></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"> </span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">方法二</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">：“</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">学信网</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">”</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">微信公众号</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">获取</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">1.关注学信网微信公众号，绑定学信网账号，点击“登录学信档案”，查看“学籍学历”信息。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701794280049697.png" title="1772701794280049697.png"/>     <img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701800942088097.png" title="1772701800942088097.png"/>   </span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">2.选择“学籍信息”，点击“获取图像采集码”。</span></p><p style="text-align: start; "><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 19px; text-align: center;">                                          <img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701836068048273.png" title="1772701836068048273.png"/>     <img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701856748023874.png" title="1772701856748023874.png"/>        </span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">方法三</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">：</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">学信网APP</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px">获取</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">1.登录学信网APP点击“学籍查询”查看“学籍学历”信息。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"><img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701873151069636.png" title="1772701873151069636.png"/>        <img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701880270058373.png" title="1772701880270058373.png"/></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">2.选择“学籍信息”，进入后点击“获取图像采集码”。</span></p><p style=";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701889529018246.png" title="1772701889529018246.png"/>        <img alt="image.png" src="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/image/20260305/1772701920899061339.png" title="1772701920899061339.png"/><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 19px;"> </span></p><p><br/></p>
</div>]]></content:encoded>
